response.overview: Darron follows the rules. Fisher doesn’t even read them. When a priceless wine bottle is destroyed en route to a VIP tasting, the two vineyard employees must scramble to replace it—without getting caught. What could go wrong? A lot!  “CORKED” is a sharp, fast-paced comedy about last chances, bad decisions, and the unlikely magic of making it up as you go.
response.title: Corked
